<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>For Miss Torii 💖</title>

<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(120deg,#ff9a9e,#fad0c4);
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  overflow:hidden;
  color:white;
  text-align:center;
}

.container{
  max-width:700px;
  animation: fadeIn 4s;
}

h1{
  font-size:40px;
}

p{
  font-size:20px;
  line-height:1.6;
}

.heart{
  position:absolute;
  color:red;
  font-size:25px;
  animation: float 6s infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
  0%{transform:translateY(100vh);opacity:0;}
  50%{opacity:1;}
  100%{transform:translateY(-10vh);opacity:0;}
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
  from{opacity:0}
  to{opacity:1}
}

button{
  padding:12px 25px;
  font-size:18px;
  border:none;
  border-radius:30px;
  background:white;
  color:#ff4b6e;
  cursor:pointer;
  margin-top:20px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>💖 Hello Miss Torii 💖</h1>

<p>
The day I met you I never imagined that someone special like you would love me.  
I am so grateful and happy in my life because of you.  

You make my days special and make me feel happy and comfortable.  
You are my safe place and I never want to let you go.
</p>

<p>
I am also sorry for all my mistakes and bad behaviour.  
I promise I will try my best to make you happy and give you the life you deserve.
</p>

<p>
I never felt love before in my life, but when I met you  
I felt love for the first time. That is all I ever wanted.
</p>

<h2>THANK YOU for showing me true love 💖</h2>

<h1>I LOVE YOU ❤️ SOOOOO MUCH</h1>

<button onclick="playMusic()">Play Music 🎵</button>

</div>

<audio id="music" loop>
<source src="love.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<script>

function playMusic(){
  document.getElementById("music").play();
}

function createHeart(){
  const heart=document.createElement("div");
  heart.classList.add("heart");
  heart.innerHTML="❤️";
  heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
  heart.style.animationDuration=(Math.random()*3+3)+"s";
  document.body.appendChild(heart);

  setTimeout(()=>heart.remove(),6000);
}

setInterval(createHeart,400);

</script>

</body>
</html>
